----COMMANDS TO INSTALL ANSIBLE-----

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install software-properties-common
sudo apt-add-repository ppa:ansible/ansible
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install ansible


 SSH CONNECTION:
 
 In Master :
 Run the commands 
 1)ssh-keygen
 2)cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub
 (copy the key )
 
IN SLAVE :
1)cat >> ~/.ssh/authorized_keys
paste the key here 

Now run "SSH slave ip address" in Master



 
 
 
